sig_info: Black Cat starts the quest with 9 Combo Shield Passives which prevent her from losing Combo when struck. These persist across fights.
These Combo Shields fall off one at a time, and last for 3 second(s) after Black Cat is Struck. These Combo Shields also begin to expire after she Evades using this ability.
When Black Cat would be struck while dashing, for each Combo Shield effect on her, she has a 3.96 to 8.08% chance to gain an Evade Passive for 1 second.
